---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <div class="bg-gray-950 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Helpful Tips</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 text-center mb-16">Practical tech advice from RigRescue</p>

            <div class="space-y-8">
                <a href="/blog/tech-support-scams" class="block bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-3xl hover:bg-gray-800 transition">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">How to Spot and Remove Tech Support Scams in 2026</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">Learn the red flags and what to do if you’ve been targeted.</p>
                </a>

                <a href="/blog/build-gaming-pc" class="block bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-3xl hover:bg-gray-800 transition">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Should You Build Your Own Gaming PC in 2026?</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">Pros, cons, and when it makes the most sense.</p>
                </a>

                <a href="/blog/speed-up-slow-computer" class="block bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-3xl hover:bg-gray-800 transition">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">How to Speed Up a Slow Computer in 2026</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">Simple fixes that can breathe new life into your PC.</p>
                </a>

                <a href="/blog/best-free-antivirus" class="block bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-3xl hover:bg-gray-800 transition">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Best Free Antivirus & Security Tools in 2026</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">You don’t always need to pay for protection.</p>
                </a>

                <a href="/blog/home-network-security" class="block bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-3xl hover:bg-gray-800 transition">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Home Network Security Tips for Families</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">Protect your home Wi-Fi and connected devices.</p>
                </a>

                <a href="/blog/upgrade-pc-or-buy-new" class="block bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-3xl hover:bg-gray-800 transition">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">When Should You Upgrade Your PC vs Buy New?</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">Make the smartest decision for your needs and budget.</p>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
